<div class="article">







	Welcome to the new and improved Moguls Mountain Travel Review. Check out new features including "Hot Deals," Snow Reports from Around the Globe, News from the Mountains, and the Moguls Picture-Perfect Vacation Contest. Of course you will still find the best mountain vacation packages throughout North and South America, Europe, and New Zealand.
<P>
This week's Review introduces the Moguls Mountain Passport. This exclusive deal for Moguls travelers will let you experience the mountains from a whole new perspective this summer. Read on for more details!



</div>


